            {
              "language": "en",
              "text": "She looked down from the mountain and took a photo of the village."
            },
            {
              "language": "fa",
              "text": "او از کوه به پایین نگاه کرد و از روستا عکس گرفت."
            },
            {
              "language": "kmr",
              "text": "Wê ji çiyayê ber bi xwarê ve temaşe kir û wêneyek ji gundê girt."
            },
            {
              "language": "pl",
              "text": "Spojrzała z góry w dół i zrobiła zdjęcie wioski."
